<td class="mbox-text" style="">This article is <b>in need of attention from an expert on the subject</b>. Please help recruit one or <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Risk&amp;action=edit" class="external text" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Risk&amp;action=edit" rel="nofollow">improve this article</a> yourself. See the <a href="/wiki/Talk:Risk" title="Talk:Risk">talk page</a> for details. Please consider using {{<a href="/wiki/Template:Expert-subject" title="Template:Expert-subject">Expert-subject</a>}} to associate this request with a <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:WikiProject" title="Wikipedia:WikiProject">WikiProject</a>. <small><i>(October 2008)</i></small></td>
</tr>
